description         A GPU-rendered terminal emulator that supports inline 3D graphics

long_description    \
    {*}${description}. ${name} features a spinning rat cursor, traditional 2D \
    and 3D modes, inline 3D objects, GPU-backed text rendering, and image \
    support via the Kitty Graphics Protocol. Inspired by TempleOS and built \
    with Rust and Ratatui.

